## Step 5 – Find ALL jars containing Jackson classes

This is the most important command:

```bash
for j in BOOT-INF/lib/*.jar
do
  if jar tf "$j" 2>/dev/null | grep -q "com/fasterxml/jackson"; then
      echo "===== $j ====="
      jar tf "$j" | grep "com/fasterxml/jackson" | head -20
      echo
  fi
done
```

Paste the entire output.

