## Step 7 – Verify whether `JsonProperty.namespace()` exists

First extract the annotations jar:

```bash
mkdir -p /tmp/jackson
cd /tmp/jackson
jar xf /tmp/check/BOOT-INF/lib/jackson-annotations-*.jar
```

Then:

```bash
javap -classpath . com.fasterxml.jackson.annotation.JsonProperty | grep namespace
```

Expected output:

```text
public abstract java.lang.String namespace();
```

---

## Step 8 – Verify the same inside SBINEWPG

```bash
mkdir -p /tmp/sbi
cd /tmp/sbi
jar xf /tmp/check/BOOT-INF/lib/SBINEWPG_2023.jar
```

Then:

```bash
javap -classpath . com.fasterxml.jackson.annotation.JsonProperty | grep namespace
```

If nothing is returned, then **SBINEWPG is definitely overriding Jackson with an old version**, which matches the `NoSuchMethodError` you're getting.

